rcuisine.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif' alt=':)' class='wp-smiley' /> I&#8217;m a huge fan of your blog! I&#8217;ve loved everything I&#8217;ve made of yours. Thank you!!</p></li></ul><p class="comments_meta"><a href='http://www.natalieskillercuisine.com/2009/08/killer-brown-sugar-cookies.html/feed'><abbr title="Really Simple Syndication">RSS</abbr> feed for comments on this post.</a> <a href="http://www.natalieskillercuisine.com/2009/08/killer-brown-sugar-cookies.html/trackback" rel="trackback">TrackBack <abbr title="Universal Resource Locator">URL</abbr></a></p><h2 id="postcomment">Leave a comment</h2><form action="http://www.natalieskillercuisine.com/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform"><p><input type="text" name="author" id="author" value="" size="22" tabindex="1" /> <label for="author"><small>Name (required)</small></label></p><p><input type="text" name="email" id="email" value="" size="22" tabindex="2" /> <label for="email"><small>Mail (will not be published) (required)</small></label></p><p><input type="text" name="url" id="url" value="" size="22" tabindex="3" /> <label for="url"><small>Website</small></label></p><p><textarea name="comment" id="comment" cols="70%" rows="10" tabindex="4"></textarea></p><p><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" tabindex="5" value="Submit Comment" /> <input type="hidden" name="comment_post_ID" value="34" /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="akismet_comment_nonce" name="akismet_comment_nonce" value="d4b810febc" /></p></form>RSS</div></div></div><div id="sidebar"><div class="sidebar_wrap"><ul class="xoxo"><li id="text-5" class="widgetcontainer widget_text"><h3 class="widgettitle">About Natalie</h3><div class="textwidget"><a href="http://www.natalieskillercuisine.com/about/"><img src="http://www.natalieskillercuisine.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/Natalie_headshot.jpg"></a></div></li><li id="text-7" class="widgetcontainer widget_text"><h3 class="widgettitle">Follow Natalie